Class ButtonComponent

java.lang.Object
  com.jaunt_api.component.FormComponent
      com.jaunt_api.component.ButtonComponent

public class ButtonComponent
extends FormComponent

This class represents an HTML/XHTML button that does not by default generate a name-value pair when pressed (eg, <input type='reset'>, <input type='button'>)
